            <h5 class="column-head" data-uuid="66f3d4d64d9b452483ead52857e2456d">Boomtowns along the Erie Canal</h5>
            <p class="intro" data-uuid="3f106969592d45a5a1c56b6a90760554">Between 1820 and 1840, cities along Erie Canal prospered from commerce and their populations boomed. &#160;</p>
